<h2>Nuclear Weapons Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<h3>by Carry Sublette</h3>

<h2>Section 3.0 Matter, Energy, and Radiation Hydrodynamics</h2>
</center>
<pre>
Version 2.16
December 1, 1996 

