WORKER'S PARTY</a>   (PKK) [Iran/Syria/Iraq]<br> aka: Kurdish Labor 
Party
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/plf.html">PALESTINE LIBERATION FRONT</a> (PLF) [Tunisia/Iraq]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/plo.html">PALESTINE LIBERATION ORGANIZATION</a>   (PLO) [Tunis]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/pij.html">PALESTINIAN ISLAMIC JIHAD</a>  (PIJ) [Gaza]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/pflp-gc.html">POPULAR 
FRONT FOR THE LIBERATION OF PALESTINE-GENERAL COMMAND</a>   (PFLP-GC) [Syria]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/pflp-sc.html">POPULAR FRONT FOR THE LIBERATION OF PALESTINE SPECIAL COMMAND</a>   (PFLP-SC) [Lebanon]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/psf.html">POPULAR STRUGGLE FRONT</a>  (PSF) [Syria]
</ul>

<h3><a name="csam">CENTRAL</a> AND SOUTH AMERICA</h3>
<ul>
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/fpmr.html">EMANUEL RODRIGUEZ PATRIOTIC FRONT</a>   (FPMR) [Chile]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/fmln.html">FARABUNDO MARTI NATIONAL LIBERATION FRONT</a> (FMLN)  [El Salvador]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/mjl.html">LAUTARO YOUTH MOVEMENT</a>   <a name="mjl">(MJL)</a> [Chile]
<li>MJL (see <a href="#mjl">Lautaro Youth Movement</a>)
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/fpm.html">MORAZANIST PATRIOTIC FRONT</a>   (FPM) [Honduras]
<li>MRTA (see <a href="#tupac">Tupac Amaru Revolutionary Movement</a>)
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/elm.html">NATIONAL LIBERATION ARMY</a>   (ELM) [Bolivia]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/eln.html">NATIONAL LIBERATION ARMY</a>   (ELN) [Columbia]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/cnpz.html">NESTOR PAZ ZAMORA COMMISSION</a>  <a name="cnpz">(CNPZ)</a> [Bolivia]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/farc.html">REVOLUTIONARY ARMED FORCES OF COLOMBIA</a> (FARC) [Colombia]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/tupac.html">TUPAC AMARU REVOLUTIONARY MOVEMENT</a>   <a name="tupac">(MRTA)</a> [Peru/Bolivia]
</ul>
<h3><a name="euro">EUROPE</a></h3>
<ul>
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/grapo.html">1st OF OCTOBER ANTIFASCIST RESISTANCE GROUP</a> (GRAPO)  [Spain]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/eta.html">BASQUE FATHERLAND AND LIBERTY</a>   (ETA) [Spain/France]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/ira.html">PROVISIONAL 
IRISH REPUBLICAN ARMY</a>   <a name="ira">(IRA)</a> [Northern Ireland] <br> 
aka: The Provos
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/raf.html">RED ARMY FACTION</a>   (RAF) [Germany]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/17nov.html">REVOLUTIONARY ORGANIZATION 17 NOVEMBER</a>  (17 November)  [Greece]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/ela.html">REVOLUTIONARY PEOPLE'S STRUGGLE</a>   (ELA) [Greece]
<LI><a href="http://www.tezcat.com/~top/Terrorist/lliure.html">TERRA LLIURE</a>   (TL) (Free Land)	[Spain]
</UL>
