                   TERRORIST PROFILES


   From "The Profiles of Global Terrorism", an annual
   report published by the US State Department. These
   files were serialized as  The Terrorist Profile 
   Weekly,an email list service edited by Chris J DiBona 
   [cdibona@mason1.gmu.edu].  The list is now defunct:
   DO NOT attempt to subscribe.


  =======================================================

 All information herein is in the public domain, as derived
 from government documents at the US Department of State.
 
  =======================================================

			CONTENTS:
