Richelson, Copyright 1985, Ballinger Publishing Company, 54 Chruch 
Street, Harvard Square, Cambridge, MA., 02138-3730, ISBN 0- 88730-024-3 
(cl), 88730-025-1 (pb). and the Second Edition, Copyright 1989, ISBN 0-
88730-245-9 (0- 88730-226-2 (pb)<P>
<B>2</B>  <B><I><a href="biblio.htm#ciacult">The CIA and the Cult of Intelligence</a></B></I></a>, Victor 
Marchetti and John D. Marks, Copyright 1974, Alfred A. Knopf, New York, N.Y., Distributed by Random House, Inc., New York, N.Y. <P>
<B>3 </B> <B><I><a href="biblio.htm#secreteyes">America's Secret Eyes in Space</a></B></I>:  The U.S. 
Keyhole Spy Satellite Program", Jeffrey T. Richelson, Copyright 1990, 
Harper &amp  Row Publishers, Inc., Ballinger Division, New York, N.Y.,  
ISBN 0-88730-285-8.         <P>
