<p>
<p>
<H1>Chinese Air Force</H1>
</center>
The Chinese Air Force consists of Soviet manufactured main line aircraft, as well as Chinese manufactured aircraft  derived  from Soviet designs.  Below we list both the types of aircraft with brief statistics on them, as well as a  summary  of the deployment of these aircraft (Data on aircraft from Air Force Magazine, 1985  2):<P>
