<TITLE>Chinese Navy</TITLE>
<center>
<img src="milnetsm.gif" align=middle, alt="Milnet">
<p>
<p>
<a href="milnet.htm"><img src="milico.gif" align=middle alt="Milnet Main"></a>
<a href="military.htm"><img src="miltico.gif" align=middle alt="Military"></a>
<p>
<H1>Chinese Navy</H1>
</center>
The Chinese Navy fields a number of impressive ships, including a few but frightening 
nuclear submarines.  The Chinese had commissioned a Varyag (originally the Soviet Riga 
Class) aircraft carrier.  rumor has it now that the Chinese are trying to buy a Kiev class 
aircraft carrier, capable of launching VTOL jets &amp  helicopters, and cruise 
missiles.<P>
