<title>MILNET:  Recent Events Effecting Travellers</title>
<center>
<h1>Moscow:  2nd Bomb on Trolly Bus</h1>
</center>
<p>
A bomb left under the seat of a Moscow trolly bus seriously injured 20 riders
in Moscow on July 11, 1996.  This is the 2nd such incident in as many days.
Moscow authorities have announced a crackdown on "undesirables in the city".
Increased police action in the city is thought to not bode well for travellers
as tensions rise.  Please see the official U.S. State Department 
<a href="http://travel.state.gov/russia_announce.html">travel warning</a> for
Russia.

