<H1>OneStep Internet Services Provider Services - We Create Your Web Pages</h1>
<p>
 Designing and implementing your own home page may not be high on your list of tasks to spend your valuable time on.  For a very reasonable fee, OneStep Internet Services will take the job on.  All we need is your ideas on what you want the web pages to look like.  We can operate in one of five modes:
<p>
<ol>
<b><li></b>You give us a complete storyboard and detailed description of what you want us to build (in terms of who, what, and when). Note that if you want, we can help manage your storyboard developoment, facilitating between all the interested folks in your company.
<b><li></b>You select from our library of sample Home Pages and we customize to your identity. 
<b><li></b>Number 2 above with the inclusion of 10, 40, or 80 hours of upgrade/maintenance.
<b><li></b>Assign one or more employees to work with us for 10, 40, 80, or 160 hours of design and development of your web pages.
<b><li></b>You give us a general idea of what you wish us to build, and when you need it leaving all the creative to us..  We will schedule, at a minimum of two review sessions to measure progress and allow you to redirect our efforts as necessary.
</ol>
<p>
For more information on how we can help you with the writing of your home pages write us email at:
<p>
<p>
<hr>
<address><b>InServices@onestep.com</b></address></pre>
