<TITLE>MILNET:  Intelligence Agencies - Interpretation</TITLE>
<center>
<img align=middle src="milnetsm.gif" alt="Milnet">
<p>
<p>
<a href="milnet.htm"><img alt="Milnet Main" align=middle src="milico.gif"></a>  <a href="intell.htm"><img alt="Intell" align=middle src="intell.gif"></a></center>
<p>
<p>
<H1>MILNET:  Intelligence Interpretation</h1>
<p>
<b>Intrepretation:</b>  The process of making rational conclusions based upon
the <a href="analysis.htm">analysis</a> of <a href="collecti.htm">collected</a> 
intelligence.  The intrepretation can be anything from discerning a particular
shape in a photograph to mean a silo has been captured on film, to making a
judgement that a particular activity or event has some new or special impact on 
other events, countries, or even world activity. 
<p>

</DOC>
