Mnemonic   Service Name                     Branch                     Country </b>             
AMAN       Agaf Modiin (Intelligence        Production Branch          Israel
             Branch of Israeli Defense
             Forces) Pure Military only

BND        Bundesnacrichtendienst           Division II                West
             (Federal Intelligence          Evaluation                 Germany
             Service)

