N.Y., 10020.  <P>
ISBN 0-671-60117- 2.<P>
6.  <B><I>The U.S. Intelligence Community</B></I>, Jeffry T. Richelson, 
Copyright 1989, Ballinger Publishing Company, 54 Church Street, Harvard 
Square, Cambridge, Massachusetts, 02138.  ISBN 0-88730-226-2<P>
